{"TopicId":221431,"ForumId":208,"TopicTitle":"AP/PE markers too small at higher resolutions and don\u0027t scale with UI scale changes [AP/PE markers stay the size of 1080p markers so end up tiny]","CreatedByName":"jclovis3","CreatedById":188635,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T10:45:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jclovis3","CreatedById":188635,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T10:45:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 Home 22H2 Build 19045.3803 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 7 7800X3D | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0MSI Gaming GeForce RTX 4080 16GB GDDR6X PCI Express 4.0 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E128 GB DDR5-6000\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCPU: AMD Ryzen 7 7800X3D\u003Cbr\u003E\nGPU: MSI Gaming GeForce RTX 4080\u003Cbr\u003E\nResolution: 3840x2160 (16:9)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI play on a 48\u0022 TV that sits 6 feet on front of me on account of being far sighted. At this resolution, which is native to the TV, I find the font sizes of map labels like AP/PE markers to be way too small and changing the UI scale has no effect on this. When I change the resolution to\u00A01920x1080 (16:9) the font for these labels is great. The aspect ratio does not change so the font size should not change either. The whole point of higher resolutions isn\u0027t for bigger screen sizes that you still sit up close to. It\u0027s for greater image detail. Objects aren\u0027t made smaller, so the text should not either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022pnhX5ba.jpg\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/pnhX5ba.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-24T10:36:34Z\u0022 title=\u002212/24/2023 10:36  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 24\u0022\u003EDecember 24, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-20T20:48:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/188635-jclovis3/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022188635\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/188635-jclovis3/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jclovis3\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I have seen this. Can you supply a screenshot to show people how small they are at that resolution?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jclovis3","CreatedById":188635,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T11:04:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022pnhX5ba.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/pnhX5ba.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Peacock","CreatedById":224498,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T11:22:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/188635-jclovis3/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022188635\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/188635-jclovis3/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jclovis3\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thanks, added it to your report!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T11:40:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/188635-jclovis3/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022188635\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/188635-jclovis3/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@jclovis3\u003C/a\u003E Thank you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}